      <title>子弹世界--又一个过渡</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/02/bulletWorld/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/02/bulletWorld/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="面向对象设计一个子弹世界的基本结构"><a href="#面向对象设计一个子弹世界的基本结构" class="headerlink" title="面向对象设计一个子弹世界的基本结构"></a>面向对象设计一个子弹世界的基本结构</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">selef</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    dadadada初始化常规</span><br><span class="line">    self.world = BulletWorld()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 创建一个3d世界，该世界有很多物理现象，物理钢体，物理载体</span></span><br><span class="line">    按键处理代码</span><br><span class="line">    添加全局事件代码</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">update</span>()</span><br><span class="line">按键随时间响应代码</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">updateWorld</span>()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建世界物理实体(重中之重)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">实例化代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>整体结构如上</p><h3 id="如何创建各种钢体呢？"><a href="#如何创建各种钢体呢？" class="headerlink" title="如何创建各种钢体呢？"></a>如何创建各种钢体呢？</h3><h5 id="面向代码对象思考"><a href="#面向代码对象思考" class="headerlink" title="面向代码对象思考"></a>面向代码对象思考</h5><ul><li>钢体类的属性：形状类，重量</li><li>钢体类的方法：设置重量形状</li><li>在细想panda3d绑定节点才能渲染，所以要用世界节点绑定钢体类</li><li>纵向往上想添加实体是世界的方法</li></ul><h5 id="构建代码"><a href="#构建代码" class="headerlink" title="构建代码"></a>构建代码</h5><ol><li><p>构建钢体的形状（类）</p><figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">球面：<span class="constructor">BulletSphereShape(<span class="params">radius</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line">平面：<span class="constructor">BulletPlaneShape(Vec3(法向量)</span>,厚度)</span><br><span class="line">方体箱子：<span class="constructor">BulletBoxShape(Vec3(<span class="params">dx</span>, <span class="params">dy</span>, <span class="params">dz</span>)</span>)</span><br><span class="line">圆柱体： <span class="constructor">BulletCylinderShape(<span class="params">radius</span>, <span class="params">height</span>, ZUp)</span></span><br><span class="line">圆锥体： <span class="constructor">BulletConeShape(<span class="params">radius</span>, <span class="params">height</span>, ZUp)</span></span><br><span class="line">胶囊形体： <span class="constructor">BulletCapsuleShape(<span class="params">radius</span>, <span class="params">height</span>, ZUp)</span></span><br><span class="line">注意ZUp表示旋转轴 属于panda3d.Bullet.ZUp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>绑定钢体类BulletRigidBodyNode(name)使得成为节点</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">coneNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Cone&quot;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其实这可以拆分成多个步骤，创建钢体，给钢体添加形状，绑定钢体成为一个节点， 等同于</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">box_shape = BulletBoxShape(Vec3(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>))</span><br><span class="line">box_node = BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Box&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">box_node.addShape(box_shape)</span><br><span class="line">box_np = render.attachNewNode(box_node)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改钢体节点物理属性（不说了），钢体属性设置，附加给世界</p><table><thead><tr><th>方法</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>setMass(kg)</td><td>设置重量区别</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">coneNp.setPos(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">coneNp.node().setMass(<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">coneNp.node().addShape(coneShape)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="键盘处理方式"><a href="#键盘处理方式" class="headerlink" title="键盘处理方式"></a>键盘处理方式</h2><h3 id="一种是简单的回调函数，按一次动一次"><a href="#一种是简单的回调函数，按一次动一次" class="headerlink" title="一种是简单的回调函数，按一次动一次"></a>一种是简单的回调函数，按一次动一次</h3><figure class="highlight axapta"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">accept(<span class="string">&quot;keyname-pressType&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">str</span> functionName)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 注意使用回调函数的的函数名不要加()</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta"># 原因是？？？以后会知道的</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第二种是加入到实时加载刷新函数内，方式1是把上面的方法写到update()函数里面。</p><p>方式2是使用InputState(str 标记变量，str keyName)类进行储存</p><p>set(str 标记变量)进行检验是否有按键</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">inputState.watchWithModifiers(<span class="string">&#x27;forward&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">inputState.watchWithModifiers(<span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">inputState.watchWithModifiers(<span class="string">&#x27;reverse&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;s&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">inputState.watchWithModifiers(<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;d&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">inputState.watchWithModifiers(<span class="string">&#x27;turnLeft&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;q&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">inputState.watchWithModifiers(<span class="string">&#x27;turnRight&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;e&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在update函数体内：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">processInput</span>(<span class="params">self, dt</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 初始化力和力矩向量</span></span><br><span class="line">   force = Vec3(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   torque = Vec3(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 判断事件按键存在否</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> inputState.isSet(<span class="string">&#x27;forward&#x27;</span>): force.setY( <span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> inputState.isSet(<span class="string">&#x27;reverse&#x27;</span>): force.setY(-<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> inputState.isSet(<span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span>):    force.setX(-<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> inputState.isSet(<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>):   force.setX( <span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> inputState.isSet(<span class="string">&#x27;turnLeft&#x27;</span>):  torque.setZ( <span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span> inputState.isSet(<span class="string">&#x27;turnRight&#x27;</span>): torque.setZ(-<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置单位力和力矩</span></span><br><span class="line">   force *= <span class="number">30.0</span></span><br><span class="line">   torque *= <span class="number">10.0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 箱子添加活跃，不知道什么用</span></span><br><span class="line">   self.boxNP.node().setActive(<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">#应用力和力矩</span></span><br><span class="line">   self.boxNP.node().applyCentralForce(force)</span><br><span class="line">   self.boxNP.node().applyTorque(torque)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这东西以后拿来直接用就好了，一般只需修改单位力和单位力矩</p><h3 id="例子源码"><a href="#例子源码" class="headerlink" title="例子源码"></a>例子源码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">124</span><br><span class="line">125</span><br><span class="line">126</span><br><span class="line">127</span><br><span class="line">128</span><br><span class="line">129</span><br><span class="line">130</span><br><span class="line">131</span><br><span class="line">132</span><br><span class="line">133</span><br><span class="line">134</span><br><span class="line">135</span><br><span class="line">136</span><br><span class="line">137</span><br><span class="line">138</span><br><span class="line">139</span><br><span class="line">140</span><br><span class="line">141</span><br><span class="line">142</span><br><span class="line">143</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> sys</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> direct.directbase.DirectStart</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.bullet <span class="keyword">import</span> ZUp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> direct.showbase.DirectObject <span class="keyword">import</span> DirectObject</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> direct.showbase.InputStateGlobal <span class="keyword">import</span> inputState</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> AmbientLight,PointLight</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> DirectionalLight</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> Vec3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> Vec4</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> Point3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> TransformState</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.core <span class="keyword">import</span> BitMask32</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.bullet <span class="keyword">import</span> BulletWorld</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.bullet <span class="keyword">import</span> BulletPlaneShape,BulletConeShape</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.bullet <span class="keyword">import</span> BulletBoxShape,BulletSphereShape,BulletShape,BulletCylinderShape</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.bullet <span class="keyword">import</span> BulletRigidBodyNode,BulletCapsuleShape</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> panda3d.bullet <span class="keyword">import</span> BulletDebugNode</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Game</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">DirectObject</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 初始化配置</span></span><br><span class="line">        base.setBackgroundColor(<span class="number">0.1</span>, <span class="number">0.1</span>, <span class="number">0.8</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        base.setFrameRateMeter(<span class="literal">True</span>)  <span class="comment"># 用来打开右上角计算帧率的函数</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 摄像头位置</span></span><br><span class="line">        base.cam.setPos(<span class="number">0</span>, -<span class="number">20</span>, <span class="number">4</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        base.cam.lookAt(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># Light</span></span><br><span class="line">        alight = AmbientLight(<span class="string">&#x27;ambientLight&#x27;</span>)  <span class="comment"># 能照亮空间中同时所有点的光源。这类型的光实际上不需要是场景图的一部分，因为它没有有意义的地位。</span></span><br><span class="line">        alight.setColor(Vec4(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">1</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        alightNP = render.attachNewNode(alight)  <span class="comment"># 设置一个结点，为了之后可以对齐进行操作</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        dlight = DirectionalLight(<span class="string">&#x27;directionalLight&#x27;</span>)  <span class="comment"># 从无限远的特定方向发出的光，就像阳光一样。</span></span><br><span class="line">        dlight.setDirection(Vec3(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>))  <span class="comment"># 设置灯光指向的方向。</span></span><br><span class="line">        dlight.setColor(Vec4(<span class="number">0.3</span>, <span class="number">0.3</span>, <span class="number">0.3</span>, <span class="number">1</span>))  <span class="comment"># 设置灯光的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">        dlightNP = render.attachNewNode(dlight)  <span class="comment"># 设置结点</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 可能配套使用，只有用了clearLight这一条，才能设置光在节点上</span></span><br><span class="line">        render.clearLight()</span><br><span class="line">        render.setLight(alightNP)  <span class="comment"># 设置光在结点上</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># render.setLight(dlightNP) #设置光在结点上</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 按键</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.accept(<span class="string">&quot;escape&quot;</span>,self.doExit)</span><br><span class="line">        self.accept(<span class="string">&quot;w&quot;</span>,self.turnUp)</span><br><span class="line">        self.accept(<span class="string">&quot;a&quot;</span>,self.turnLeft)</span><br><span class="line">        self.accept(<span class="string">&quot;d&quot;</span>,self.turnRight)</span><br><span class="line">        self.accept(<span class="string">&quot;s&quot;</span>,self.turnBack)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#     加载更新</span></span><br><span class="line">        taskMgr.add(self.update,<span class="string">&quot;update&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 加载世界部件模型</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.updateWorld()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">update</span>(<span class="params">self,task</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        dt = globalClock.getDt()</span><br><span class="line">        self.world.doPhysics(dt)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> task.cont</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">updateWorld</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.worldNp = render.attachNewNode(<span class="string">&quot;World&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        self.debugNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletDebugNode(<span class="string">&quot;Debug&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        self.debugNp.show()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        self.world = BulletWorld()</span><br><span class="line">        self.world.setGravity(Vec3(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, -<span class="number">9.81</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        self.world.setDebugNode(self.debugNp.node())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 钢体模型</span></span><br><span class="line">        groundShape = BulletPlaneShape(Vec3(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>),<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        groundNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Ground&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        groundNp.node().setMass(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 钢体节点的node函数返回钢体对象，钢体对象有addShape()方法，用面向对象的思维去思考问题</span></span><br><span class="line">        groundNp.node().addShape(groundShape)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        boxShape = BulletBoxShape(Vec3(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.5</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Box&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.node().setMass(<span class="number">8</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.node().addShape(boxShape)</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.setPos(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        cylinderShape = BulletCylinderShape(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, ZUp) <span class="comment">#zUp为圆柱轴</span></span><br><span class="line">        cylinderNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Cylinder&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        cylinderNp.setPos(-<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        cylinderNp.node().setMass(<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        cylinderNp.node().addShape(cylinderShape)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        coneShape = BulletConeShape(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, ZUp)</span><br><span class="line">        coneNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Cone&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        coneNp.setPos(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        coneNp.node().setMass(<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        coneNp.node().addShape(coneShape)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        capsShape = BulletCapsuleShape(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, ZUp)</span><br><span class="line">        capsNp = self.worldNp.attachNewNode(BulletRigidBodyNode(<span class="string">&quot;Capsule&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        capsNp.setPos(<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        capsNp.node().addShape(capsShape)</span><br><span class="line">        capsNp.node().setMass(<span class="number">1.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        node_list = [groundNp.node(), self.boxNp.node(), cylinderNp.node(),</span><br><span class="line">                     cylinderNp.node(),coneNp.node(),capsNp.node()]</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> node <span class="keyword">in</span> node_list:</span><br><span class="line">            self.world.attachRigidBody(node)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        boxModel = loader.loadModel(<span class="string">&quot;models/box.egg&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        boxModel.flattenLight()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 盒子模型直接添加到钢体节点而不是钢体对象</span></span><br><span class="line">        boxModel.reparentTo(self.boxNp)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">doExit</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">turnUp</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.setY(self.boxNp.getY() + <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">turnLeft</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.setX(self.boxNp.getX() - <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">turnRight</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.setX(self.boxNp.getX() + <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">turnBack</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.boxNp.setY(self.boxNp.getY() - <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">game = Game()</span><br><span class="line">base.run()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content>
      
      
