      <title>调试类相关</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/01/%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95%E7%B1%BB/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/01/%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95%E7%B1%BB/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="调试类"><a href="#调试类" class="headerlink" title="调试类"></a>调试类</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># World 调试辅助线节点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># BulletWorld(&quot;typeName&quot;) #该typeNameb不是随便的节点名，是固定的</span></span><br><span class="line">self.debugNP = self.worldNP.attachNewNode(BulletDebugNode(<span class="string">&quot;Debug&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">self.debugNP.show()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#不知道下面是干嘛的</span></span><br><span class="line">self.debugNP.node().showWireframe(<span class="literal">True</span>)  <span class="comment">#显示线框True,默认开启</span></span><br><span class="line">self.debugNP.node().showConstraints(<span class="literal">False</span>) <span class="comment">#显示约束</span></span><br><span class="line">self.debugNP.node().showBoundingBoxes(<span class="literal">True</span>) <span class="comment">#显示边界框</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">self.debugNP.node().showNormals(<span class="literal">False</span>) <span class="comment">#显示法线</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#self.debugNP.showTightBounds()</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#self.debugNP.showBounds()</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第一步：绑定一个调试对象节点</p><p>第二步：调用.show()函数，应该是对其进行初始化</p><p>第三步：调用调试节点的node()返回类的各种方法</p><blockquote class="pullquote mindmap mindmap-md"><ul><li>BulletDebugNode(“Debug”)（调试类对象）</li><li>调试类节点<ul><li>.node() &#x2F;返回的是类吧<ul><li>showWireframe(t,f)</li><li>showBoundingBoxes(t,f)</li><li>等等</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></blockquote><div class="note info no-icon flat"><p>场景类设置</p></div><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content>
      
      
      
