      <title>panda3d知识</title>
      <link href="/2022/11/28/panda3d%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/"/>
      <url>/2022/11/28/panda3d%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-0相机"><a href="#1-0相机" class="headerlink" title="1.0相机"></a>1.0相机</h1><p>先开个相机吧，也算半个眼睛，这样才能看到别人</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">base.disableMouse()  <span class="comment"># 不关的话，鼠标移动代表相机旋转</span></span><br><span class="line">self.camera.setPos(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">100</span>)  <span class="comment"># ShowBase（）的camera赋值为相机类</span></span><br><span class="line">self.camera.setHpr(<span class="number">0</span>, -<span class="number">90</span>, <span class="number">0</span>) <span class="comment">#相机镜头角度设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#等同于self.camera.lookAt(x, y, z) </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/11/28/zayqh9.png" alt="相机由天空向地面照相"></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">base.disableMouse()</span><br><span class="line">base.setBackgroundColor(<span class="number">.3</span>, <span class="number">.3</span>, <span class="number">.3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">camera.setPosHpr(<span class="number">4</span>, -<span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">15</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/11/28/zaybtJ.png" alt="相机正对熊猫"></p><h1 id="2-0理解节点"><a href="#2-0理解节点" class="headerlink" title="2.0理解节点"></a>2.0理解节点</h1><ul><li><p>节点就是各种类对象（场景类，演员类，光照类，声音类）等等</p></li><li><p>各种节点只要插入树中才能被渲染器渲染</p></li><li><p>树根是render</p></li><li><p>各种节点的物理参数以父节点为准，如节点（0,0,5）的位置是相对父节点而言的</p></li></ul><h2 id="2-1节点的常见函数方法"><a href="#2-1节点的常见函数方法" class="headerlink" title="2.1节点的常见函数方法"></a>2.1节点的常见函数方法</h2><table><thead><tr><th>函数名</th><th>相关说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>setPos(x, y, z)</td><td>位置配置</td></tr><tr><td>setX(), setY(), setZ()</td><td>单独设置</td></tr><tr><td>getPos(x, y, z)</td><td>获得位置</td></tr><tr><td>getX(), getY(), getZ()</td><td>单独获得位置</td></tr><tr><td>setScale(bi,bili, bili)</td><td>放缩比例</td></tr><tr><td>setHpr(x, y, z)</td><td>三维旋转</td></tr></tbody></table><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content>
      
      
